To create the api files in a files: 
1- go in the files
2- Git bash
3- npm init
4- click "Enter" until the question "Is this OK? (yes)"


To add the libraries to your small project before starting to work on it
1. npm install express
2. It will add 50 packages and create a node_modules files

Never push the node modules thoses files on git



When you want to use the library, you go on the website